defaultWhat impact will the devolution in 2015 of funding to Local Transport Bodies and the introduction of the Single Local Growth Fund have?
defaultIt will wipe out any consideration of sustainable transport schemes 
defaultboth 
defaultbig and small.   That is because it is designed to promote jobs
default supported by road building
default.  
default&#xa0;
defaultHowever, the 
defaultpurpose
default of creating employment is to increase the wealth and 
defaultwell being
default of 
defaultthose in an area.  The cost 
default/
default benefit ratio of sustainable transport can bring significant economic benefits if factors, such as quality of life, well-being and basic health are admissible 
defaultas equals in the discussion. 
