defaulthe West Sussex Cycle Forum (WSCF).   
default&#xa0;
defaultThe WSCF was established to 
defaultrepresent and support
default the views of the various local cycling forums around the county. Whereas local cycle forums act locally and practically, the WSCF is a strateg
defaultic partner for the local forums and is recognised by West Sussex County Council as a 
defaultconsultee
default.
default&#xa0;
defaultIts aim - as in its constitution is:
defaultTo work towards the creation of conditions in West Sussex so that cycling is perceived as a valid and reasonable choice ofdefault transport for both utility and leisure purposes.   default&#xa0;
